WEBVTT

00:00.451 --> 00:01.320
What is in the bag?

00:01.907 --> 00:02.809
An old sweater.

00:03.311 --> 00:04.235
What color is it?

00:04.944 --> 00:05.737
Yellow.

00:06.179 --> 00:07.043
What is it made of?

00:07.597 --> 00:07.967
Wool?

00:08.383 --> 00:08.917
Cotton?

00:14.301 --> 00:14.933
Wool.

00:15.525 --> 00:16.529
It is made of wool.

00:16.686 --> 00:18.219
Hmm, very nice.

00:18.565 --> 00:19.261
Thank you.

00:20.466 --> 00:21.412
What is that?

00:22.914 --> 00:24.749
It's a present for you.

00:25.371 --> 00:27.525
Oh, what is it?

00:28.501 --> 00:29.377
You have to guess.

00:29.611 --> 00:30.903
Oh, I don't know.

00:32.313 --> 00:33.659
What shape is it?

00:34.731 --> 00:36.239
It's square.

00:37.780 --> 00:40.022
No, it's round.

00:43.596 --> 00:44.481
Can I help you?

00:44.935 --> 00:46.175
How much is that t-shirt?

00:46.549 --> 00:47.984
It's 15.60.

00:48.245 --> 00:49.719
Sorry, how much did you say?

00:49.938 --> 00:51.127
15.60.

00:51.445 --> 00:53.927
And how much are those mugs?

00:54.086 --> 00:58.376
The big mugs are 10.25 and the small ones are 8.75.

